title: The Pocket Rocket
description:
The Pocket Rocket is a performance oriented mini cruiser designed to give you snappy turning and versatility in a small package. With the right amount of concave, an ergonomic standing platform, and a true kicktail, this mini cruiser won't set any limits on your skateboarding.

L: 26.00"
W: 7.75"
WB: 14.00"

The Pocket Rocket comes in either a Hawaiian Koa topsheet or Bamboo topsheet, with art by Eric Waetzig.
